  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Get in, get out, get paid.\"</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore vast cities as a getaway driver and shoot twin-stick style while escaping the law.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player driving and shooting action </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up crew members and drive them around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can be played in  3rd person view or bird's eye camera view</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 handcrafted levels: Devil's Plains, Misty Fields, Sunny Coast, Martin's Valley, Motor Bay, Golden Sands, Magpie Island, Suburbia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgradeable cars with skill points and guns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special perk items alter every run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take screenshots in Photo Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus level: Survival challenge Arena</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pumping soundtrack by DKSTR</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect achievements and compete on leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Get in, get out, get paid.\"</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore vast cities as a getaway driver and shoot twin-stick style while escaping the law.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player driving and shooting action </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up crew members and drive them around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can be played in  3rd person view or bird's eye camera view</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 handcrafted levels: Devil's Plains, Misty Fields, Sunny Coast, Martin's Valley, Motor Bay, Golden Sands, Magpie Island, Suburbia</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgradeable cars with skill points and guns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special perk items alter every run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take screenshots in Photo Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus level: Survival challenge Arena</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pumping soundtrack by DKSTR</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect achievements and compete on leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
